{"tid":2305891,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"玩物達人●轉身變美少女...  Cosplayer裝「胸」作勢一條龍","createTime":"2020-11-30T04:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T19:59:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ea908fbc81d022aeccd4374c061698b31e39a3","tid":2305891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20201130/FN6ILL4YNRBGXLH3RWXNRLZW54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20201130%2FFN6ILL4YNRBGXLH3RWXNRLZW54%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=f352363a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20201130%2FFN6ILL4YNRBGXLH3RWXNRLZW54%2F&h=98abdf35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20201130/FN6ILL4YNRBGXLH3RWXNRLZW54/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n玩物達人●轉身變美少女... <br />\nCosplayer裝「胸」作勢一條龍<br />\n<br />\n角色扮演（cosplay）是一群愛好動漫遊戲的人，穿上動漫服裝扮演當中的角色，這種次文化由日本傳至香港，由九十年代流行至今，亦發展出一套本地cosplay文化與風氣。她叫火雞，原名吳美琪，是一名有十多年資歷的cosplayer，見證着近十年香港cosplay界的變遷，多年來她都堅持自己一手一腳製作服裝道具，從零開始cosplay。<br />\n<br />\n約三十歲的火雞愛cosplay也愛手作，「cosplay的道具，我會當成是模型般去做。小時候已經會剪紙做道具，例如畫出美少女戰士的變身器，剪出來再貼在身上扮變身。」中學時，因家政課接觸了縫紉技巧，再靠裁縫工具書自學，學會了畫紙樣和做衫。後來她修讀設計課程，一出糧就花了$2,700買一部衣車，目的就是自製手袋。機緣巧合下，她接觸到cosplay，「某次朋友拜託我製作一套visual rock系服裝，完成後覺得很漂亮，也想幫自己做一套。由於我很喜歡《Final Fantasy》的角色，所以當時就製作了《FFX》女主角Yuna的服裝出席cosplay活動。」火雞從此踏上cosplayer之路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拒絕現成貨 親手做質素更高<br />\n<br />\n現職櫥窗設計的火雞，因公認識了不同種類的材料和製作技巧，並應用在cosplay服裝和道具上。例如她向我們展示的《FF VII Remake》女角Tifa造型，看似簡單，原來有很多複雜細節，「Tifa這套衫大部份都是仿皮物料製成，像吊帶、腰帶和裙是不同質感的仿皮，並壓上花紋。手環、手套和手甲都用了EVA膠製作，手套上有壓花圖案再加窩釘；手甲上的文字則要逐個壓花，而且會加上一些戰損塗裝，看起來更有金屬感。」另外，火雞亦展示了一個以forex board物料製作的萬聖節燈，還有以熱縮片製成、帶火燄效果的頭髮，十分專業。<br />\n<br />\n近年cosplay的門檻越來越低，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n性感無傷大雅 「是個人的選擇」<br />\n<br />\n既然手藝與技術被認同，會否考慮將cosplay製作成為職業呢？火雞表示不可能，因香港市場太細，「在香港比較困難，如果在日本或台灣會比較容易。」<br />\n<br />\n對於近年有少數女cosplayer走性感路線以不同形式賺錢，她表。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n興趣歸興趣，有人以cosplay賺錢，火雞。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火雞示範《FF VII Remake》Tifa的cosplay，看似簡單的衣裝，原來有不少細節，令製作難度大大提升。<br />\n<br />\n火雞有時會cosplay性感的角色，如這個Super Sonico造型，就要戴假胸「裝胸作勢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sl2_Q5JSBFQ1fihk0pjVMJHS3JI=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GWAJN3OZMRBBTNS3QT4AP56WQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsl2_Q5JSBFQ1fihk0pjVMJHS3JI%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGWAJN3OZMRBBTNS3QT4AP56WQI.jpg&h=45491a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然手藝與技術被認同，但火雞不會考慮成為全職手作人，「在香港比較困難，如果在日本或台灣會比較容易。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火雞也有cosplay近年大熱動漫《鬼滅之刃》的角色胡蝶忍，連夢幻般的背景，也是她自己製作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她手持的燈以forex board物料製成，再在底部加上LED燈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sKZbOUIBlvh3Yela1C4UhKm5mVI=/4521x4443/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LXYFFET6FZD5FHOL3TKLSI3DMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsKZbOUIBlvh3Yela1C4UhKm5mVI%3D%2F4521x4443%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLXYFFET6FZD5FHOL3TKLSI3DMI.jpg&h=0572be13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《THE IDOLM@STER》高垣楓cosplay服裝，上身是馬甲，下身是宮廷的裙襬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0jBAQu3VIDs11RyqPiIDZFXlI_8=/3927x4396/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KB5CEPFH6ZDEJC7IAL57CAXWTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0jBAQu3VIDs11RyqPiIDZFXlI_8%3D%2F3927x4396%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKB5CEPFH6ZDEJC7IAL57CAXWTA.jpg&h=6c239379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這套是《死亡愛麗絲》的愛麗絲服裝，上身有不少暗花，而且要用上金色仿皮包邊，長短不一的裙腳也令裁剪難度增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火雞會找一些愛好拍攝cosplayer的相熟攝影師朋友為她拍照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如角色有紋身，火雞會先在電腦繪製圖案，再找製作公司印在絲襪上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次出動前，火雞都花不少時間在化妝及裝身，連假髮也要造型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q-CuErctJ-vnpoulqtT-oECJ4qQ=/6651x4434/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RABZPZ6L4RCTFOQM34TINL6EGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ-CuErctJ-vnpoulqtT-oECJ4qQ%3D%2F6651x4434%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRABZPZ6L4RCTFOQM34TINL6EGA.jpg&h=ff072750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這個像火的配飾其實是熱縮片，用風筒就可吹成火的形狀。<br />\n<br />\n記者：馬子聰<br />\n<br />\n攝影：潘志恆、伍永健<br />\n<br />\n部份圖片由受訪者提供"},{"pid":"ce8e5af674d5faf4fdeb5f8eb82946f3c1906bfc","tid":2305891,"uid":25100,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"啲衫又整得幾靚"},{"pid":"b5175c278bfac48bc9b288c267178ea681daf848","tid":2305891,"uid":48026,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"諗住入黎睇偽娘裝假狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedf331a702aed074fe5238ffe19d624945bd5ef","tid":2305891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqmMyPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqmMyPZ.jpg&h=4bd9f5d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f493ac36a7b772cd4911c2dd3bf01dd02539b76d","tid":2305891,"uid":12417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"係幾靚"},{"pid":"6ddd63ff6da2f812e42b44f9ce3d1d5e88572c12","tid":2305891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ce8e5af674d5faf4fdeb5f8eb82946f3c1906bfc","tid":2305891,"uid":25100,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"啲衫又整得幾靚"},"citedB